		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷斧进行至多3段的4种普通攻击：<br/><span color="#bfffeb">旋-劈</span><span>；</span><span color="#bfffeb">挑-劈</span><span>；</span><span color="#bfffeb">旋-旋-劈</span><span>；</span><span color="#bfffeb">挑-旋</span><span>；每段攻击都造成</span><span color="#b9b9b9">50%</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffacff">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="739" y="447" width="423" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">当雷斧的斧子存在附魔，而玩家又距离比较远时，雷斧从地里挖出两种史莱姆丢出：雷史莱姆造成<span color="#ffacff">62.5%</span><span>伤害，变异雷史莱姆造成</span><span color="#ffacff">75%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="671" width="434" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷斧横拿斧子转圈圈，触碰造成<span color="#b9b9b9">12.5%</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffacff">12.5%</span><span>伤害，持续3s，旋转结束后施放尾刀，造成</span><span color="#b9b9b9">50%</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffacff">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="926" width="423" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#99ffff">(仅雷雨天、秘境)<span color="#ffffff">雷斧举起斧子，马上被雷电晕，并在其周围电击造成</span><span color="#ffacff">50%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害，总共被电2次，然后雷斧躺下。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="671" width="439" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#bfffbf">(仅附魔)<span color="#ffffff">雷斧用力将斧子往地上砸，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">50%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害，顺势将自己挑起，然后落地坐下，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">75%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害。<br/></span><span color="#df3df2">强攻强化：</span><span color="#ffffff">落地时周围产生3道落雷，每道造成</span><span color="#ffacff">50%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="447" width="439" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffbfbf">(仅强攻强化)<span color="#ffffff">距离玩家较远时，雷斧拿着斧子跳起来下落，造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">100%</span><span color="#ffffff">/</span><span color="#df99ff">100%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害。若斧子附带</span><span color="#df99ff">雷附魔</span><span color="#ffffff">，则周围产生5道落雷，每道造成</span><span color="#df99ff">50%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="426" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷斧从地里挖出雷史莱姆，给斧子上<span textDecoration="underline">雷附魔</span><span>后丢出，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">37.5%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
