		<RichText x="66" y="1008" width="442" height="39" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷附魔：<span color="#ffacff">2雷</span><span>盾，熄灭后斧子只能打出物理伤害。该状态下，抗打断0.8。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
